item.title: Imperial iGEM success
item.author: Elsa Sotiriadis,Che Muhammad Farhan Che Abdullah,
item.description: It was a truly triumphant success for Imperial this November at MIT in Boston, where the iGEM world championship took place. iGEM, first launched in 2004, is the most prestigious and largest undergraduate competition in synthetic biology worldwide.
